# Sprint 3 Planning
**Yale Dining Hall Comparison Platform**  
**Team:** alex-the-lion  
**Sprint Duration:** November 12 - November 19, 2025 (1 week)  
**Planning Date:** November 11, 2025

---

## Sprint Goal

**"Deliver a functional MVP deployed to staging that supports a complete end-to-end user journey with working UI/UX improvements, stable staging deployment, and integration of core filtering and data pipeline features ahead of Sprint 4."**

### Success Criteria
- Unified menu comparison table displays real scraped data
- Meal period and dietary filters are fully functional
- Mobile-responsive design works across devices (375px+ width)
- Staging environment is deployed and accessible at yale-dining-staging.onrender.com
- Automated scraper runs daily and logs errors appropriately
- At least one complete user journey is demonstrable end-to-end

